yto-downloader/
├── LICENSE
├── README.md
├── requirements.txt
├── yto_downloader/
│   ├── __init__.py
│   ├── main.py          # Main GUI app script
│   ├── downloader.py    # yt-dlp wrapper + download logic
│   ├── gui.py           # GUI classes and UI code
│   └── utils.py         # Helpers (e.g. base64 icon, splash screen)
├── assets/
│   └── (if you want to add images/icons externally)
└── tests/
    └── test_downloader.py  # Unit tests (optional)

main.py — entry point that runs the app.

downloader.py — functions/classes to handle yt-dlp downloads, options, progress hooks.

gui.py — tkinter GUI classes, widgets, event handlers.

utils.py — utility functions, embedded icons, splash screen code.

requirements.txt — Python dependencies (yt-dlp, Pillow, etc.).

assets/ — external images/icons if you want to load from files instead of base64.

tests/ — automated tests if you want to add them.
